<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>DX.GROUPING is an application that allows generic heirarchical group structures to be defined. Group id's defined in DX.GROUPING may be used to group DX.CUSTOMER records into entities for reporting or revaluation purposes.</p>
        </ovdesc>
<ovimage></ovimage>
</overview>
