<t>
<field>DX.GROUPING</field>
<desc>
            <p>The ID of the DX.GROUPING file allows the user to set up heirarchical group structures of derivatives customers.</p>
            <p>The structure of the ID is as follows:</p>
            <table border="0">
                <tr>
                    <td>AAA</td>
                    <td />
                    <td>Top level group</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>AAA.BBB</td>
                    <td />
                    <td>Group - member of group AAA</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>AAA.BBB.CCC</td>
                    <td />
                    <td>Group - member of group AAA.BBB</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>When the relevant group ID is attached to a DX.CUSTOMER record using the field GROUP, that customer becomes a member of that group (and by extension a member of any 'parent' groups of which the group is itself a member.</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p>Alphanumeric, maximum 35 characters</p>
            <p>Period separated key</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>GEN.DATA.CODE</field>
<desc>
            <p>Code or symbol representing the group for reporting purposes in the process named in GEN.DATA.NAME.</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p>Up to 15 characters of free format text</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>GEN.DATA.LIMIT</field>
<desc>
            <p>Limit figure or other input data referring to the group that may be required by the process named in GEN.DATA.NAME.</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p>Up to 11 numerical characters</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>GEN.DATA.NAME</field>
<desc>
            <p>Name of a report or process that will be updated using the group information.</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p>Up to 15 characters </p>
            <p />
            <p>There must not be more than one occurrence of each item         within a group hierarchy.</p>
        </desc>
